# Resource_And_Economy

## 1. Applies when
There are resources, inventory, trading, crafting, maintenance, camp consumption,
currency, or an economic loop.

## 2. This document owns
Resource classification; materials; consumables; inventory; trading; prices; drop
rates; economic loop; maintenance materials; camp consumption.

## 3. This document does NOT own
Combat energy numbers (Gameplay_Systems); narrative collectibles (Collectibles);
mission text; map structure.

## 4. Recommended chapter structure
1. Document role & design phase · 2. Resource classification · 3. Combat supply ·
4. Equipment materials · 5. Camp supply · 6. Mission resources ·
7. Trading & maintenance · 8. Acquisition & consumption · 9. Economy & board · 10. TODO

## 5. Common boundaries
- Resource vs Collectibles — resources/materials vs narrative relics.
- Resource vs Gameplay — inventory/supply vs combat energy formula.
- Resource vs Crafting — materials vs recipes (survival genres).

## 6. Common audit rules
- Material table is single authority; recipes not duplicated.
- Ordinary resources must not be maintained inside Collectibles.
